{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1975,"month":2,"day":12}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"军民共读马列书","authors":["郭德贵"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜家家静无声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然风雨惊睡梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农老李忙坐起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见外屋灯正明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红星眼里亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！连长读书在用功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左手轻轻翻书页，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右手挥笔兴冲冲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沏壶茶，香又浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茧手托出一片情："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“连长呵！喝茶润润嗓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿讲给咱听听。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大爷心似浓茶热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻把咱放心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱要努力学人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攻读马列攀高峰！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心欢跳，热血涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大爷搬出一条凳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民灯下同学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两腔话儿吐心声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“革命路上不歇脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿云破雾学雄鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马列利剑握在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戳穿反动阶级复辟经！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“文化大革命绘宏图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政记心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨里磨刀刀更快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续革命打冲锋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读呵读，攻呵攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风更大呵雨更猛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风大雨猛灯不熄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得心里红彤彤！”"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}